+# P4.8 — latency-contract silence TTL expiry + re-notify escalation
+
+P4.8 extends the P4.7 notifier silence workflow with automatic expiry handling:
+
+- a silence window can expire naturally without manual `unsilence`
+- if the gate is still active at expiry time, notifier marks the silence as `ttl_expired`
+- an audit event is written to `ops:latency_contract:events:v1`
+- Telegram/ops-summary reminder resumes with escalated severity (`page`)
+- gate enforcement is unchanged; this only affects notification flow
+
+## New env knobs
+
+- `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_NOTIFY_PAGE_STREAM=notify:telegram:page`
+- `LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_NOTIFY_ESCALATED_REMINDER_S=3600`
+
+## Redis state
+
+Per-purpose silence state (`cfg:orderflow:latency_contract:deploy_lint:silence:<purpose>`) now stores:
+
+- `ttl_expired_ts_ms`
+- `ttl_expiry_notify_count`
+- `ttl_expiry_last_notify_ts_ms`
+- `last_action=ttl_expired`
+
+Notifier state (`metrics:latency_contract:deploy_lint:notifier:last`) now stores:
+
+- `expired_purposes_csv`
+- `expired_purposes_count`
+- `escalation_active`
+- `last_emit_severity`
+
+## Expected event flow
+
+1. operator runs `ack` / `silence`
+2. purpose is suppressed until `silence_until_ts_ms`
+3. timer fires after expiry and gate is still active
+4. notifier emits `latency_deploy_lint_ack_silence_ttl_expired`
+5. notifier emits `latency_deploy_lint_silence_ttl_expired_reactivated`
+6. reminders continue on page severity cadence until fixed or re-acked
+
+## Metrics
+
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_ttl_expired{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_ttl_expired_age_seconds{purpose}`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_summary_expired_gate_active_total`
+- `latency_contract_deploy_lint_notifier_escalated`
+
+## Quick checks
+
+```bash
+redis-cli HGETALL metrics:latency_contract:deploy_lint:notifier:last
+redis-cli HGETALL cfg:orderflow:latency_contract:deploy_lint:silence:meta_cov_rollout_controller
+python3 -m orderflow_services.latency_contract_deploy_lint_silence_v1 status --purpose meta_cov_rollout_controller
+curl -fsS http://localhost:${LATENCY_CONTRACT_DEPLOY_LINT_EXPORTER_PORT:-9834}/metrics | grep latency_contract_deploy_lint_notifier_escalated
+```
